Author: Javin1342
Title: üíπ[ANN][AIRDROP][ICOBENCH 4,9] SRT | TOKEN BACKED BY PROFITABLE OIL BUSINESSüíπ
Body: Dear friends and community of SRT Coin!  This message is meant to inform all members of our community, all bounty program participants, our partners and SRT Coin tokenholders. October 25 is the scheduled day of SRT Coin first round purchase completion. Unfortunately, because of difficult situation on the cryptocurrency market, the project hasn`t yet raised the softcap to launch our refineries production. We highly appreciate your support for the project and trust in it; therefore, we feel our responsibility to develop and put on the market a product of the highest possible level.  We get many words of support and high ratings of our project from various people around the world. And it inspires us to achieve this goal, overcome obstacles and work hard to get success and unlock the incredible potential of blockchain technology in the fuel industry. We also believe that there are many people in the world who share our vision with us on SRT Coin project.  In this regard, we have decided to extend the sale of tokens until December 25, 2018. We plan to evaluate changes in the project team and its strategy and hold negotiations on the issue of raising funds with venture funds.  We provide an additional 30% bonus to all tokenbuyers as a measure of support for our community in this difficult period of development of the market and cryptocurrencies. Bonuses will be credited to all buyers of tokens automatically. Stay in touch, we will regularly inform you about all the changes and news.  Also, we have a news about bounty and airdrop campaigns.  Bounty campaign is closing today. No more media campaign applications will be accepted. All past applications were proceeded, rewards are added. Final bounty rewards spreadsheet will be available in a few days.  Airdrop will be extended until December 25, 2018, rules for joining are the same.

Today we`ll talk about LAUNCHING an industrial plant with a capacity of 36m3 / day.    Main features of this unit: 1. The raw material can be any gasoline fractions with low octane and high sulfur content (65 RON and 180 ppm). Our next step - Decentralised network of small oil refineries creation.
